All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Deprecated public class IHSColorSpaceJAIExt extends IHSColorSpaceImageNExt
Deprecated.
This class is a subclass of IHSColorSpaceImageNExt to work around serialization issues. It is deprecated and you're not supposed to use it anymore. It is only kept around for backward compatibility. Won't be removed anytime soon, in order to support long term serialization of ImageLayout descriptions.
